list.item:
convey seriousness of our objection, i.e. our willingness to alter
                                current or contemplated 

                                actions if our interests are ignored;

avoid calling into question our support for Yugoslav non-alignment
                                in Europe, i.e. Yugoslav independence from the USSR, especially in the risky
                                post-Tito period;

maintain US influence in and with
                                Yugoslavia and, conversely, not afford the Soviets opportunities to
                                expand their influence;
